---
---

<section class="personas" id="who" aria-labelledby="personas-heading">
  <div class="personas-intro" data-animate>
    <p class="kicker">Teams</p>
    <h2 id="personas-heading">Built for teams that ship AI</h2>
    <p class="sub">
      Whether you're writing the agent or directing it, Amprealize gives everyone on the team a shared language for what works.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="personas-grid" data-animate style="transition-delay: 60ms">
    <article class="persona persona--dev">
      <div class="persona-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="22" height="22">
          <path d="M8 18l-4-4 4-4M16 6l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Developer</h3>
      <p>
        Capture patterns from your best runs, version them like code, and stop re-solving the same problems across sessions.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>CLI + VS Code native workflow</li>
        <li>Behavior library with semver</li>
        <li>MCP tool parity for automation</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="persona persona--pm">
      <div class="persona-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="22" height="22">
          <path d="M4 6h16M4 12h10M4 18h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Product Manager</h3>
      <p>
        Track what agents are doing, keep execution aligned with intent, and ship without needing to read the logs yourself.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Projects + boards for agent work</li>
        <li>Behavior approval workflows</li>
        <li>Audit-friendly execution trail</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="persona persona--ba">
      <div class="persona-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="22" height="22">
          <path d="M8 5h8v14H8V5Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
          <path d="M10 9h4M10 13h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Business Analyst</h3>
      <p>
        Write behaviors in plain language, attach them to processes, and let the team reuse them without asking engineering for help.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Human-readable behavior format</li>
        <li>Compliance checklist integration</li>
        <li>Usage reports per project</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="persona persona--ent">
      <div class="persona-icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="22" height="22">
          <path d="M12 4l8 4v8l-8 4-8-4V8l8-4Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
          <path d="M8 10h8M8 14h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Enterprise</h3>
      <p>
        Deploy on your infrastructure, enforce governance from day one, and keep every AI action traceable to a person and a policy.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Self-hosted Docker + Helm</li>
        <li>SAML SSO + RBAC</li>
        <li>SOC 2–ready audit logs</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .personas {
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: var(--landing-section-y, clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px));
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  }

  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .personas {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .personas-intro {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .kicker {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .personas-intro h2 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 2.4vw + 0.5rem, 2.35rem);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
  }

  .sub {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    max-width: 42ch;
  }

  .personas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .persona {
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(70, 108, 140, 0.18);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    align-content: start;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--persona-accent, var(--color-accent));
    transition:
      transform var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-spring-gentle),
      border-color var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out-quart);
  }

  .persona--dev {
    --persona-accent: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .persona--pm {
    --persona-accent: var(--color-accent-secondary);
  }
  .persona--ba {
    --persona-accent: var(--color-info);
  }
  .persona--ent {
    --persona-accent: #1a5f8a;
  }

  .persona:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-border-hover);
  }

  .persona-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    color: var(--persona-accent);
  }

  .persona h3 {
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  .persona p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.58;
  }

  .persona ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .persona li + li {
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .personas-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
